description: Darkness and strange smells waft around in this alleyway, strange

33624.name: The Eastern Path In The Graveyard
description: Twisted and ancient gravestones pass by you as you walk the beaten path
of this graveyard.  The sky is dark, large, black clouds overhead seem to
not move.  A wind blows from no where, which seems very cold.  The path
continues on its twisted journey in the graveyard.  Most of the graves here
seem to have been dug up, and empty caskets lie around.

33611.name: The Graveyard of Zozo
description: Two large, stone gargoyls great you at the gates.  They look like they
are going to rip you into peices.  A pair of wrought iron gates leads into

ancient ones, standing, mostly tipped to one side, and rough with age.  The
graveyard is to the north.

33607.name: The Dirt Path
description: The Unknown Forest.  The woods around you seem tight, enough that is
would not be a smart thing to walk through them.  No sign of life makes its
presents known, the only thing living besides you, are the trees.  The trees
overhand the road, blocking all light from the sun or the moon, depending if
its day or night, do you remember what time is was?  Behind you is the dirt
path, ahead of you is the dirt path.

33600.name: a skeleton warrior~
description:
The skeleton warrior is a large, animated skeleton. He wears only
a few peices of armor, and the rest are bones.
33600.room_name: A skeleton warrior of the Army Of Darkness stands here.

33601.name: Oderus~
description:
Oderus is a very large creature. His face, looks like rotting flesh,
as does the rest of his body. Hair sprouts up from diffrent places
and the cuddlefish hangs between his leg. On his shoulders he wears
large spiked shoulder guards. In his hand, he holds a very large sword.
33601.room_name: Oderus stands here, watching over his Army Of Darkness.
